1
00:00:28,875 --> 00:00:33,250
PERTEMBUNGAN KECIL YANG RAPAT

2
00:00:43,416 --> 00:00:45,500
Baiklah, bantuan sudah tiba.

3
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:48,875
Bertenang. Semuanya baik-baik saja.

4
00:00:49,375 --> 00:00:51,875
Ikut saya. Kita pasti sempat balik makan.

5
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:56,915
Saya nak pergi.

6
00:00:56,916 --> 00:00:57,958
Jangan dekat.

7
00:00:58,833 --> 00:01:01,582
Manusia, kami datang dengan aman.

8
00:01:01,583 --> 00:01:06,624
Jauh perjalanan kami,
tapi kami gembira berada di sini.

9
00:01:06,625 --> 00:01:07,625
Dia ada pistol!

10
00:01:12,375 --> 00:01:13,208
Aduhai.

11
00:01:14,291 --> 00:01:16,083
- Hei, ia hidup!
- Kejar!

12
00:01:18,666 --> 00:01:19,875
Aduh, gila betul!

13
00:01:22,791 --> 00:01:24,041
Mari sini! Tak guna!

14
00:01:25,791 --> 00:01:27,458
Tak guna, ia masih hidup!

15
00:01:51,458 --> 00:01:53,958
Ini semakin bagus. Seronoknya.

16
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:56,666
Ya, kau memang cantik.

17
00:01:58,750 --> 00:02:00,333
Aku nak minum sikit.

18
00:02:02,458 --> 00:02:05,749
Jangan hirau aku. Aku cuma nak...

19
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:07,750
Ya Tuhan! Alamak. Tuhan!

20
00:02:12,333 --> 00:02:14,625
Lepaskan aku!

21
00:02:15,375 --> 00:02:18,791
Apa jadah? Alamak! Tidak!

22
00:02:22,958 --> 00:02:24,957
Mereka di sini!

23
00:02:24,958 --> 00:02:27,000
Mereka buru kita semua!

24
00:02:30,625 --> 00:02:31,624
KEDAI BAHAN LUCAH

25
00:02:31,625 --> 00:02:34,666
Tidak, tunggu! Ambil aku!

26
00:02:55,541 --> 00:02:58,708
TETAP TENANG DAN TERUSKAN SAHAJA

27
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:08,290
WIRA PERANG NEGARA ASING

28
00:03:08,291 --> 00:03:09,708
Angkat! Masukkan.

29
00:03:10,416 --> 00:03:11,540
Celup.

30
00:03:11,541 --> 00:03:12,833
Langgar!

31
00:03:13,333 --> 00:03:15,999
Ya! Ayuh! Rasakan!

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,999
KEDAI ARAK GREYFRIAR

33
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,625
Kau boleh pergi jahanam!

34
00:03:22,833 --> 00:03:24,666
Pergi jahanam!

35
00:03:26,458 --> 00:03:28,583
Bantai mereka. Bantai habis-habisan!

36
00:03:32,708 --> 00:03:37,375
NEGARA-NEGARA BERSATU BUMI

37
00:03:59,291 --> 00:04:00,208
Cepat!

38
00:04:09,875 --> 00:04:12,250
Belum lagi! Pergi!

39
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:33,333
Tidak!

40
00:04:36,833 --> 00:04:37,665
Sedia!

41
00:04:37,666 --> 00:04:39,582
MANUSIA BERKUASA

42
00:04:39,583 --> 00:04:41,749
Semua dah sedia, celaka!

43
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:44,457
CUBA USIK INI

44
00:04:44,458 --> 00:04:48,833
BUKAN PLANET KAU

45
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,875
Terjemahan sari kata oleh NNorhan

